text: ohuge janaya aturin ( satyya) pratiksepa kala, paramanta dinaye hamu va (gæna) boru kala, tavada melova jivitayehi ovunata dayadayan pirinæmu pradhanihu "mohu numbala men minisaku misa næta, numbala anubhava karana dæyin ohu da anubhava karayi. numbala panaya karana dæyin ohu da panaya karayi" yæyi pævasuvoya
